result.title: Ural Championship 2016 (for those who have not played)
result.content:
Hi everyone.

We would like to invite you to participate in contest based on Ural Championship 2016 problems that will take place on timus on 4 June, 11:00 Moscow time. Please don't participate in this contest if you have already solved these problems during the onsite contest or it's Internet-mirror.
